        "heading_text": "The People Behind <em>Diamond Affaire</em>",
        "description": "<p>Our team is the heart of Diamond Affaire, bringing together diverse expertise to create jewelry that is as unique as the individuals who wear it. Bharat Gupta, our manufacturing head based in India, began his journey in the diamond jewelry industry with an education at GIA in Carlsbad and IDI in Surat. Driven by a dream to create high-quality, affordable jewelry, Bharat has achieved success by delivering pieces that are both exquisite and accessible. Prachi Gupta, our designer and curator, combines her passion for fashion and creativity with industry expertise. Entering the world of diamonds, Prachi brings a unique design sense that together with skilled craftsmanship, aims to bring unparalleled elegance through our creations.Our factory is based in Surat, India, where over 100 artisans use their skills to create the most exquisite handcrafted pieces just for you. By setting up our factory in this developing region, we are dedicated to providing these talented artisans with sustainable livelihoods and supporting their communities.</p>",
